  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add mustard seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add spinach and cook until it is wilted.",
    "Add basmati rice and stir to combine with the spinach mixture.",
    "Add coconut cream, chickpeas, and salt, and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover the saucepan.",
    "Simmer for 15 minutes or until the rice is cooked and the liquid is absorbed."
